<h2>Visibility Toggle</h2>
<p>
    This started as a Dropdown component, but was generalized to a Visibility Toggle.
    A Visibility Toggle consists of a trigger, some content, and the component gaining or losing an attribute when the trigger is interacted with.
</p>

